Version 1.0beta2 - released 2016-06-04
* fixed bug where new galleries can't be created
* fixed bug where new galleries did not properly check if the image folder exists
* fixed bug where preloading was visible on IE 11
* fixed bug where galleries were sometimes shown as thumbnails

Version 1.0beta1 - released 2016-05-27
* lifted PHP requirement to 5.3.0
* added PHP finfo extension requirement
* fixed bug where non existing gallery caused crash
* fixed bug where captions weren't shown in thumbnail nav mode
* fixed bug where magic_quotes_gpc=On caused malfunctions
* updated to Fotorama 4.6.4
* added German localization and manual

Version 1.0alpha1 - released 2015-05-26
* initial release
